  %section.speaker-alt

    %h2 Shay Howe

    %aside.group

      %img.speaker-img(src="assets/img/shay-howe.jpg" alt="Shay Howe")

      %p As a designer and front end developer, <a href="http://shayhowe.com/">Shay Howe</a> has a passion for solving problems while building creative and intuitive products. Shay specializes in product design and interface development, specialties in which he regularly <a href="http://learn.shayhowe.com/" rel="nofollow">writes and speaks</a> about. Currently he is the Director of Product at Belly, helping build the world's best loyalty program. Additionally, Shay helps co-organize <a href="http://chicagocamps.org/" rel="nofollow">Chicago Camps</a>, Refresh Chicago, and UX Happy Hour.

      %p
